      <p>Florida capital industry expansion accelerated post-2020 with Apollo + Blackstone + Ares + Owl Rock + Sixth Street + Oaktree Florida office growth. Substantial professional relocations from NY + CT + CA. Brickell + Coral Gables + Palm Beach office leasing. Long-term tailwind supporting practice expansion.</p>

